	(208,352,1,'Bicycle Film Festival — last call for submissions',NULL,'In 2001, cyclist Brendt Barbur was hit by a bus while riding in New York City. He insisted on turning this negative experience into a positive one, and founded <a href=\"http://www.bicyclefilmfestival.com/\">The Bicycle Film Festival</a>, a platform to celebrate the bicycle through music, art and, of course, film.\n\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3lc-lEYOLk&amp;feature=youtu.be\n\nFilm-makers, it\'s not too late to submit your entry for 2012 — roll camera and <a href=\"http://www.bicyclefilmfestival.com/submit\">submit your entry</a> by April 14th.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2018-08-31 13:11:48','2018-08-31 13:11:48','6b848142-6af7-4569-93ea-6a8cc686b11f',NULL),
