	(269,413,1,'Flat-free tires from @acme',NULL,'\n\nHate punctures? You might love this — Acme are raising funds for their \'flat-free\' tyres, which are completely airless, and should last for at least 3,000 miles.\n<blockquote><em>These tires weigh more than traditional tires, and ride like a tire with 60 pounds of air in it. They will add about 1400 grams to each wheel. You will NEVER have to fix a flat. Get up in the morning, hop on your bike to the coffee shop and work. Go for a ride on the weekend. You will never have to carry a pump, patch kit, call a friend, or walk home from the middle of nowhere because you got a flat.</em></blockquote>\n<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1065313751/cme-flatfree-bicycle-wheelsets\">Make a pledge on Kickstater</a> and for $280 you can claim one of the first sets of wheels they make.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-784\" title=\"f0718c5bc14d9fdf7fdb84cb41fcd333_large\" src=\"http://www.cyclelove.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/f0718c5bc14d9fdf7fdb84cb41fcd333_large.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"724\" />',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'2018-08-31 13:11:53','2018-08-31 13:11:53','2e745a8d-f7cd-4b23-8300-97fc00116bdb',NULL),
