	(367,'field',2,1,' those cycle crazy folk at bikeminded are on the hunt for a short film to inspire people to change from two feet to two wheels which raises the question how would you persuade a friend or loved one to start cycling when i moved to london it took me six months to pluck up the courage to start commuting by bike i couldn t see past the supposedly terrifying buses that i saw cyclists sandwiched between but with all of my friends nagging me about it eventually i bought a second hand number and started cycling fast forward a few months and i owned three bikes cycled to work daily and even rode london to brighton just for the hell of it non cyclists that s something you might not understand yet cyclelove was christened so because i want to get people on bikes by showing them they don t have to be afraid and as any good psychologist will tell you fear is the opposite of love armed with some simple facts about the road and holding your position on it no one should be intimidated by the thought of cycling update a brilliant suggestion from i speak bike cyclelovehq i ve been taking friends out on the back of my tandem and showing them their commute route so they can see how easy it is jude brosnan ispeakbike april 19 2012 '),
