	(368,'field',2,1,' designed by anna haupt and terese alstin at the faculty of engineering at lund university in sweden hovding is a personal airbag for cyclists bicycling is something we do every day and there s a sense of freedom that goes with it although people are well aware of the risks on the roads the vast majority are choosing to bicycle without a helmet when it comes down to it people do really want to protect their heads in road accidents but there are limits it isn t the bicyclists who need to change it s the product hidden inside a waterproof collar around your neck hovding is trigged by abnormal movement inflating in 1 10 of a second to almost encase the wearer s head however we re not sure what happens if you should land on your face cynicism aside however it s not often that the worlds of cycling safety and cycling fashion collide and hovding proves that it is possible to be stylish and protected '),
